gomodel:SYNGO_298  a      owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Prohibitin-2 (as well as Prohibition) copurifies with protein fractions highly enriched in docked synaptic vesicles. It is 5 - 9 fold enriched in docked SV vs. free SV.. Experimental description: To isolate docking complexes from rat brain, we first prepared synaptosomes and subjected them to limited proteolysis to dissociate pre- and postsynaptic membranes (Figure 1A). p. 286" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
